# Azure AI Foundry credentials (YOU configure these — see Step 0 in README.md)
# 1. Deploy GPT-4o in Azure AI Foundry (ai.azure.com)
# 2. On the deployment page, set SDK dropdown to "Azure AI Inference SDK"
# 3. Copy the endpoint from the code sample and Key from the left panel
#
# IMPORTANT: Copy the endpoint exactly as shown in the Foundry code sample.
# It may look like one of these depending on your resource:
#   https://<your-resource>.openai.azure.com/openai/deployments/gpt-4o
#   https://<your-resource>.services.ai.azure.com/models
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com/openai/deployments/gpt-4o
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-4o
